cu.explanation_en: Setting the ciphering algorithm to the unknown enum 'nea9' will cause negotiation failure during the security negotiation phase and NAS registration rejection.

du.explanation_en: Setting the downlink carrier bandwidth to 1000 PRBs exceeds the maximum allowed bandwidth for the frequency band and may cause configuration errors or hardware incompatibility.
du.explanation_zh: 將下行載波頻寬設定為 1000 PRB 超過頻帶允許的最大頻寬，可能導致配置錯誤或硬體不相容。
